# Testing & Quality

No test harness yet. When adding tests:

| Area | Tool |
|------|------|
| Client | Vitest + React Testing Library |
| Server | Vitest + supertest; mock Mongoose in unit tests |

Test hooks and API modules before page snapshots.

Run `npm run lint` in `client/` after frontend changes.

## Do Not

- Add trivial or mock-only tests
- Add a test runner without `package.json` scripts
